"  CAKE LAYERS:","1 1/2 cups sugar","1 cup butter, softened","4  large eggs, at room temperature","3 cups all-purpose flour","2 tablespoons unsweetened cocoa","2 teaspoons pumpkin pie spice","1 cup buttermilk","1 teaspoon baking soda","1 1/2 cups seedless blackberry jam","1 tablespoon vanilla extract","1 1/2 cups finely chopped toasted pecans","1 cup peeled and grated Granny Smith apple (about 1 large)","  Shortening","  CARAMEL-CREAM CHEESE FROSTING:","2  (8-oz.) packages cream cheese, softened","1/4 cup butter, softened","2  (13.4-oz.) cans dulce de leche","  to 4 Tbsp. whipping cream"